Package it.polimi.GC13.enums

Enum Class Resource

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Resource>
it.polimi.GC13.enums.Resource
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Resource>, Constable
public enum Resource extends Enum<Resource>
Enum representing different types of resources in the game.
  • NULL - Represents the hidden corner of a playable card.
  • EMPTY - Represents an empty corner of a playable card.
  • ANIMAL - Represents an animal reign resource.
  • FUNGI - Represents a fungi reign resource.
  • INSECT - Represents an insect reign resource.
  • PLANT - Represents a plant reign resource.
  • INKWELL - Represents an inkwell object resource.
  • MANUSCRIPT - Represents a manuscript object resource.
  • QUILL - Represents a quill object resource.
Provides methods to check if a resource is a type of reign (animal, fungi, insect, plant) or an object (inkwell, manuscript, quill), and a custom string representation with ANSI escape codes for color highlighting.
